                        <img class="shadow img-fluid" type="button" src="/images/business3.jpg" alt="" width="100%" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#img-modal" data-bs-name="business3.jpg">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <hr>
                <div class="row p-3">
                    <div class="col-md-7 order-md-1">
                        <h2 class="text-primary">5G 빅데이터를 이용한 제조지능 서비스</h2>
                        <p class="lead">
                            내용을 모르겠어요
